}}</ref>, {{lang-en|Breast Cancer Resistance Proteine}} (BCRP) <ref name="dewiki131">{{статья
| автор         = Cooray HC, Blackmore CG, Maskell L, Barrand MA.
| заглавие      = Localisation of breast cancer resistance protein in microvessel endothelium of human brain
| ссылка        = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12438926?dopt=Abstract
| издание       = Neuroreport
